{"text_id":193997,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Help"," Your"," Au","tistic"," Child","\n\n","Supporting"," an"," autistic"," child"," can"," be"," a"," profoundly"," rewarding"," experience",","," but"," it"," is"," also"," accompanied"," by"," unique"," challenges","."," With"," appropriate"," strategies",","," consistency",","," and"," unconditional"," love",","," you"," can"," help"," your"," autistic"," child"," navigate"," the"," world"," more"," effectively","."," Here"," are"," some"," essential"," tips"," to"," keep"," in"," mind",":","\n\n","##"," Maintain"," Consistency","\n","Establishing"," and"," maintaining"," a"," consistent"," routine"," is"," fundamental","."," Au","tistic"," children"," thrive"," on"," predictability","."," Set"," regular"," times"," for"," activities"," like"," meals",","," school",","," therapy",","," and"," bedtime","."," A"," visual"," schedule"," or"," calendar"," can"," help"," your"," child"," understand"," and"," anticipate"," daily"," events",".","\n\n","##"," Avoid"," Making"," Un","necessary"," Changes",","," Especially"," in"," What"," Your"," Child"," Perce","ives"," as"," Their"," Domain","\n","Unexpected"," changes"," can"," be"," distressing"," for"," autistic"," children","."," Try"," to"," minimize"," alterations"," to"," their"," environment"," or"," routine","."," If"," changes"," are"," unavoidable",","," prepare"," your"," child"," in"," advance"," with"," clear"," and"," specific"," explanations",".","\n\n","##"," Use"," Natural"," or"," Full"," Spectrum"," Lighting"," Whenever"," Possible","\n","Lighting"," conditions"," significantly"," impact"," sensory"," sensitivities","."," Full"," spectrum"," or"," natural"," lighting"," is"," the"," most"," comfortable"," and"," can"," reduce"," over","stim","ulation","."," Fluorescent"," lights"," often"," flicker",","," which"," can"," be"," bothers","ome"," or"," even"," painful"," for"," some"," autistic"," children",".","\n\n","##"," Consider"," No","ises"," in"," the"," Environment","\n","Be"," mindful"," of"," noise"," levels","."," Sounds"," that"," seem"," normal"," to"," you",","," like"," a"," humming"," refrigerator"," or"," loud"," TV",","," can"," be"," highly"," distracting"," or"," overwhelming"," for"," an"," autistic"," child","."," Use"," noise","-","cancel","ing"," headphones"," or"," find"," quieter"," alternatives"," to"," create"," comfortable"," living"," spaces",".","\n\n","##"," Let"," Them"," Retreat"," to"," a"," Quiet"," Area"," When"," They"," Want"," To","\n","Respect"," your"," child","'","s"," need"," to"," retreat"," into"," a"," calmer"," space","."," Design","ate"," a"," quiet"," area"," in"," your"," home"," where"," they"," can"," relax"," and"," de","compress","."," Personalized"," items",","," such"," as"," favorite"," toys"," or"," books",","," can"," make"," this"," space"," more"," inviting",".","\n\n","##"," Ensure"," Safety"," Around"," Your"," Home","\n","Safety"," is"," paramount","."," Secure"," dangerous"," items"," out"," of"," reach"," and"," use"," locks"," or"," alarms"," if"," necessary"," to"," prevent"," your"," child"," from"," wandering","."," Learn"," about"," their"," specific"," safety"," needs"," and"," address"," them"," proactively",".","\n\n","##"," Understand"," Sti","mming","\n","Sti","mming"," (","self","-","stim","ulatory"," behavior",")"," is"," a"," common"," way"," for"," autistic"," children"," to"," regulate"," their"," sensory"," input"," and"," express"," emotions","."," Understand"," what"," sti","mming"," behaviors"," serve"," for"," your"," child",";"," they"," often"," provide"," comfort"," and"," should"," not"," be"," discouraged"," unless"," harmful",".","\n\n","##"," Understand"," the"," Importance"," of"," Special"," Interests","\n","Special"," interests"," can"," be"," incredibly"," enriching"," for"," your"," child","."," En","couraging"," these"," interests"," can"," help"," build"," confidence"," and"," provide"," joy","."," Whether"," it","\u2019","s"," trains",","," animals",","," or"," art",","," integrate"," their"," special"," interests"," into"," daily"," activities"," as"," much"," as"," possible",".","\n\n","##"," Expect"," Different"," Body"," Language","\n","Au","tistic"," children"," often"," communicate"," differently","."," Be"," aware"," of"," nonverbal"," cues",","," such"," as"," eye"," contact",","," facial"," expressions",","," or"," body"," movements","."," Understand"," that"," these"," cues"," may"," not"," follow"," typical"," patterns"," and"," learn"," to"," read"," your"," child","'","s"," unique"," ways"," of"," expressing"," themselves",".","\n\n","##"," Know"," the"," Signs"," of"," Sensory"," Overload","\n","Recogn","izing"," the"," signs"," of"," sensory"," overload"," can"," prevent"," mel","td","owns","."," Symptoms"," may"," include"," distress",","," covering"," ears",","," complaining"," about"," noise"," or"," light",","," or"," withdrawing","."," Employ"," calming"," techniques",","," such"," as"," quiet"," time"," or"," tactile"," toys",","," when"," necessary",".","\n\n","##"," Check"," Up"," on"," the"," Child","'","s"," Health"," with"," Their"," GP"," Regularly","\n","Regular"," health"," check","-","ups"," are"," crucial"," for"," monitoring"," your"," child","'","s"," overall"," well","-","being","."," Discuss"," any"," behavioral"," or"," physical"," health"," concerns"," with"," their"," General"," Practitioner"," to"," provide"," the"," best"," possible"," care",".","\n\n","##"," Speak"," to"," Your"," Child"," Often","\n","Commun","icate"," actively"," with"," your"," child","."," Even"," if"," they"," are"," non","-","verbal",","," engage"," them"," in"," conversation","."," Use"," clear",","," concrete"," language"," and"," be"," patient","."," Communication"," fosters"," understanding"," and"," trust",".","\n\n","##"," Encourage"," Communication",","," Verbal"," and"," Otherwise","\n","Support"," all"," forms"," of"," communication","."," This"," includes"," sign"," language",","," picture"," exchange"," communication"," systems"," (","P","ECS","),"," or"," other"," assis","tive"," technologies","."," Celebrate"," any"," progress"," and"," adapt"," strategies"," to"," meet"," their"," evolving"," needs",".","\n\n","##"," Make"," It"," Clear"," that"," the"," Word"," \u201c","No","\u201d"," Is"," Important","\n","Set"," boundaries"," firmly"," but"," kindly","."," Au","tistic"," children"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," importance"," of"," the"," word"," \"","no","\""," for"," their"," safety"," and"," well","-","being","."," Provide"," clear"," explanations"," and"," suitable"," alternatives"," to"," help"," them"," understand"," limits",".","\n\n","##"," Explain"," the"," Rules",","," and"," the"," Behavior"," that"," You"," Expect","\n","Lay"," out"," rules"," and"," expectations"," clearly","."," Use"," simple"," language"," and"," visual"," aids"," to"," explain"," acceptable"," behaviors","."," Consistent"," reinforcement"," helps"," them"," grasp"," and"," adhere"," to"," these"," guidelines",".","\n\n","##"," Understand"," the"," Use"," of"," Visual"," Stim","uli","\n","Visual"," aids"," can"," be"," highly"," effective"," for"," autistic"," children","."," Picture"," schedules",","," flashcards",","," and"," visual"," markers"," can"," simplify"," communication"," and"," enhance"," understanding","."," Customizable"," visual"," tools"," tailored"," to"," your"," child","'","s"," preferences"," can"," be"," particularly"," beneficial",".","\n\n","##"," Find"," Fun",","," Constru","ctive"," Therapies"," that"," Help"," Your"," Child"," Grow","\n","Explore"," various"," therapies"," and"," activities"," that"," align"," with"," your"," child","\u2019","s"," interests","."," Occupational"," therapy",","," music"," therapy",","," and"," social"," skills"," groups"," can"," be"," both"," enjoyable"," and"," developmental",".","\n\n","##"," Recognize"," that"," Autism"," is"," Lif","elong","\n","Accept"," a